{{ArticleNow|Holocaust|[[Image:Pile-o-jews.JPG|left|100px]]

'''The Holocaust''' was a really sad time during World War II when the evil [[Germany|German]] [[skinhead|Nazi]]s, under [[Hitler]]'s rule, killed nearly six million of [[God]]'s chosen people, [[Jews|the Israelites]]. Some mean people [[holocaust denial|deny that the holocaust happened]]. These [[atheists]], who know not the promises of God, are called [[Anti-semitism|anti-Semites]] by all of civilized society, and are surely going to burn in [[Hell]]. ([[Holocaust|read more...]])}}

