Shame on [[User:Sokevinsays|Sokevinsays]]. Sokevinsays is probably better known by his handle "A [[rape|RAPE]] SPIDER", which clearly glorifies [[in the ass|sexual immorality]]. He may also be a [[homosexual]] or [[bisexual]], as A RAPE SPIDER has been known to approach [[ppl|people]] of either [[sex|gender]] (and even those of [[transexual|indeterminate gender]]). As this sinner clearly has no respect for the [[Bible|Commandments of God]], he has earned the dubious honor of being labeled "[[furry|sinner of the month]]".
